    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cups of various forms designed for drinking wine, made of glass, metal, or ceramic. The bowl may rest on a stem; the cup may have a lid.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
